result.name: Tak Hing Restaurant

reviews.text:
Since I wrote my last review, gave it 3 stars, went there several times. Bad experience since. Can understand why people hated it.
There were cockroaches crawling around. The chicken wings I used to love were still juicy and tasty but you can also taste the oil that had been repeatedly used for frying.
Had a very bad waiter last time, arrogant and unhelpful. Won't go there again. I pay for food and service!
Cold filipino beer with Hong Kong food is best to close the day
Omelette with rotten and smelly ham, which meets its standard of service
Utensils and tables are not cleaned up.  The staff won’t care.  The hygiene definitely is in question.

This review is for the Lucky Plaza branch, not to be confused with the one at Hilton Plaza. They have 3 stores that serves different types of HK style food, and I've tried 2. Decent breakfast sets and wonton noodles. Great milk tea. I would come here whenever I want a light lunch/brunch. Cheap eats in Shatin center.

result.name: 德興餐廳

reviews.text: 呢間餐廳收銀態度差，無禮貌回答客人問題非常晦氣,豆豉雞啲雞翼竟然有一束雞翼毛，都唔知有無清洗乾淨,衛生問題應重大考慮，今晚喺去希爾頓中心茶餐晚飯，食到一肚氣，下次唔會再光顧
這個茶餐廳在沙田，已經有很長時間，亦光顧了很多次，無論是食物品質、服務態度和座位舒適程度，都只是中規中矩，一般都是在附近，下午想不到吃什麼，做偶爾吃一次。
58蚊一個粟米班飯，只有兩舊魚，今次唔知唔緊要，一次貨仔，唔會再幫來，同埋會廣告朋友以免被宰客
一閒普通自助式茶餐廳，價錢正常食物一般無驚喜。

Since I wrote my last review, gave it 3 stars, went there several times. Bad experience since. Can understand why people hated it.
There were cockroaches crawling around. The chicken wings I used to love were still juicy and tasty but you can also taste the oil that had been repeatedly used for frying.
Had a very bad waiter last time, arrogant and unhelpful. Won't go there again. I pay for food and service!
